            "ratingValue": "3",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This annual fest was something different than the usual annual day. Appreciate all the efforts put in by teachers and the kids. But since we have attended the usual annual day in the past 2 years, we had high expectations as they were well organized, lighting, set ups, costumes, etc everything was superb. That was missing in this annual fest. First thing first because of costumes the coordination was missing. Parents would have complained that you charged high for the costumes. But you can always rent the costumes and take money from parents as it would not be that expensive. If the school is conducting any fucntion then they are responsible to arrange the costumes which has been done in the past but rented costumes would make more sense. So it's a request that next year onwards please conduct the usual annual day which happened in the past.Thanks.",
